290
00:22:05,656 --> 00:22:07,624
And the only way
that's gonna happen

291
00:22:07,658 --> 00:22:11,219
is if I "make the room."

292
00:22:11,262 --> 00:22:13,958
This puts 'em down.

293
00:22:13,998 --> 00:22:15,989
This takes 'em out.

294
00:22:16,033 --> 00:22:17,591
Are you gonna come help me,

295
00:22:17,635 --> 00:22:21,196
or you gonna stand there
being all righteous and loud?

296
00:22:45,062 --> 00:22:46,859
(bell dings)

297
00:22:55,506 --> 00:22:57,633
What can I do to you?

298
00:22:57,675 --> 00:22:59,836
Oh, I just need a room.

299
00:22:59,877 --> 00:23:03,574
I hope you got cash.

300
00:23:03,614 --> 00:23:06,811
Damn swipey things
haven't worked since '86.

301
00:23:06,851 --> 00:23:08,614
Or was it '85?

302
00:23:09,754 --> 00:23:12,723
When was the last time
the Royals lost last place?

303
00:23:12,757 --> 00:23:14,987
I just need a room.

304
00:23:15,025 --> 00:23:18,256
It'd be better if we got one
in the back.

305
00:23:26,704 --> 00:23:28,467
Well...

306
00:23:30,408 --> 00:23:32,433
